rows.label: soul02_P0101
rows.name:
Send 'em packing!
Take it in close!

rows.label: soul02_P0102
rows.name:
They're wide open!
Let's knock 'em silly!

rows.label: soul02_P0103
rows.name:
Ready for the fun part?
Melee attacks!

rows.label: soul02_P0201
rows.name: Open fire! Follow me!

rows.label: soul02_P0202
rows.name: Mix things up! Use a buff!

rows.label: soul02_P0203
rows.name:
Let's break 'em down
and make 'em sweat!

rows.label: soul02_P0301
rows.name:
Start big! Move in
and land a hit!

rows.label: soul02_P0302
rows.name:
It's on, now! Lay down
some cover fire!

rows.label: soul02_P0303
rows.name:
I'm making a move!
Auras ready!

rows.label: soul02_P0401
rows.name: They're tough... Heal me up!

rows.label: soul02_P0402
rows.name: Dammit... We gotta beef up!

rows.label: soul02_P0403
rows.name: I need a jolt. Buff us up!

rows.label: soul02_P0501
rows.name: Damn! I ain't got time to die!

rows.label: soul02_P0502
rows.name: This is bad. Heal me! Hurry!

rows.label: soul02_P0503
rows.name:
I ain't givin' up! Gimme some
power and I'll show 'em!

rows.label: soul02_P0601
rows.name:
Sorry, guys, I'm finished...
Hit 'em hard for me!

rows.label: soul02_P0602
rows.name:
Forget about me! Just keep
punching holes in 'em!

rows.label: soul02_P0603
rows.name:
You're gonna need an aura...
Promise me...

rows.label: soul02_P0701
rows.name:
I'm doing good!
Your turn to land a hit!

rows.label: soul02_P0702
rows.name:
Yeah! It's working!
Blast that sucker!

rows.label: soul02_P0703
rows.name: Yeah! Now, cripple 'em!

rows.label: soul02_P0801
rows.name:
Busted, baby! Now close in
and seal the deal!

rows.label: soul02_P0802
rows.name:
Now! Topple 'em
with some gunfire!

rows.label: soul02_P0803
rows.name:
Yeah, baby!
Bring 'em to their knees!

rows.label: soul02_P0901
rows.name:
Concentrate your fire
on the big sucker!

rows.label: soul02_P0902
rows.name:
We're gonna need to
weaken this big boy!

rows.label: soul02_P0903
rows.name:
Who cares about their size?
Kick it into Overclock!

rows.label: soul02_P1001
rows.name:
Look at that! Follow up
with melee attacks!

rows.label: soul02_P1002
rows.name:
Got 'em! Set me up
with some cover fire!

rows.label: soul02_P1003
rows.name:
What a hit!
Try weakening them!

rows.label: soul02_P1101
rows.name: Aura activated! Your turn!

rows.label: soul02_P1102
rows.name:
Don't be an idiot!
Where's your aura?

rows.label: soul02_P1103
rows.name: Buff us up! I'm ready to go!

rows.label: soul02_P1201
rows.name: Here we go! Overclock!

rows.label: soul02_P1202
rows.name:
Let's crack some skulls.
Go into Overclock!

rows.label: soul02_P1203
rows.name:
I'll handle Overclock.
You play it safe with an aura!

rows.label: soul02_C0101
rows.name:
Don't forget about the rest!
Take the fight to them!

rows.label: soul02_C0102
rows.name:
One down. Deal with
the rest at range!

rows.label: soul02_C0103
rows.name: It ain't over yet! Let's heal up!

rows.label: soul02_C0201
rows.name:
That's how you dodge! Use
an aura to get in the zone!

rows.label: soul02_C0202
rows.name:
I'm untouchable!
But I could still use a boost.

rows.label: soul02_C0203
rows.name:
Look at these idiots. Let's
wake 'em up with some lead!

rows.label: soul02_C0301
rows.name:
I'm kicking ass! Now get in
there and smack 'em around!

rows.label: soul02_C0302
rows.name: Hell yeah! Blast 'em!

rows.label: soul02_C0303
rows.name:
Now we're talkin'!
Move in and strike!

rows.label: soul02_C0401
rows.name:
What's with the weather?
Let's get buffed up!

rows.label: soul02_C0402
rows.name:
Weather trouble!
We need an aura!

rows.label: soul02_C0403
rows.name:
Let's use the weather to
our advantage. Weaken 'em!

rows.label: soul02_C0501
rows.name:
Man, too much running!
Buff me up!

rows.label: soul02_C0502
rows.name:
God, running sucks.
Gimme a pick-me-up!

rows.label: soul02_C0503
rows.name:
Look at me go! You're gonna
need Overclock to keep up!

rows.label: soul02_C0601
rows.name:
Thanks, pal.
Now stay on 'em!

rows.label: soul02_C0602
rows.name:
Thanks! Now get back
to shooting 'em!

rows.label: soul02_C0603
rows.name:
Thanks! You set
up with an aura?

rows.label: soul02_C0701
rows.name:
Thanks, milady. How about a
little pick-me-up? Just kidding!

rows.label: soul02_C0702
rows.name:
Man, it's tough being popular!
Who wants to help me next?

rows.label: soul02_C0703
rows.name:
Nice! Don't forget to use
an aura!

rows.label: soul02_C0801
rows.name:
I'm still in this!
Let's get in their face!

rows.label: soul02_C0802
rows.name:
No giving up! Answer them
with gunfire!

rows.label: soul02_C0803
rows.name: See! Nobody's gotta heal ME!

rows.label: soul02_C0901
rows.name:
I'm in a good position!
Open fire!

rows.label: soul02_C0902
rows.name:
I think I can pin 'em down!
Take a shot!

rows.label: soul02_C0903
rows.name:
Take the high ground,
then send 'em packing!

rows.label: soul02_C1001
rows.name: That's right! Show me that belly!

rows.label: soul02_C1002
rows.name: Toppled 'em! Fire away!

rows.label: soul02_C1003
rows.name:
Cripple 'em now
while they're down!

rows.label: soul02_C1101
rows.name:
That'll hold 'em!
Now swing away!

rows.label: soul02_C1102
rows.name:
I stunned 'em! You better
not miss now!

rows.label: soul02_C1103
rows.name:
That stopped 'em! You shouldâ€”
Actually, try weakening them!

rows.label: soul02_C1201
rows.name:
This chump's just beggin'
to get chopped up!

rows.label: soul02_C1202
rows.name:
Sleep tight! Till we start
shooting you.

rows.label: soul02_C1203
rows.name:
They're in la-la land now.
Ignite 'em with a melee attack!

rows.label: soul02_C1301
rows.name:
I've got you now.
Take a swing!

rows.label: soul02_C1302
rows.name: Fire away! I'll hold 'em still!

rows.label: soul02_C1303
rows.name: Strike now! I'll restrain 'em!

rows.label: soul02_C1401
rows.name:
Hey! My Doll's in trouble.
Patch me up!

rows.label: soul02_C1402
rows.name:
Part damage? ...Whatever.
Just keep swinging!

rows.label: soul02_C1403
rows.name:
Crap! I'm hit!
Gimme cover fire!

rows.label: soul02_C1501
rows.name:
My Doll! I knew
I shoulda healed.

rows.label: soul02_C1502
rows.name:
Sweet crispy crap, they
got me! Buff us up!

rows.label: soul02_C1503
rows.name:
Son of a... We need
Overclock, stat!

rows.label: soul02_C1601
rows.name:
I ain't got the fuel for this.
Hook me up!

rows.label: soul02_C1602
rows.name:
I could use a fix!
I'm running on fumes here!

rows.label: soul02_C1603
rows.name:
I'm outta fuel!
Hey, can ya help me out?
